Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,灰雨?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那是殘雲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,準備新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那黑雲沒有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為孤零零的飄在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被人們稱為殘雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,猿之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,像臭雞蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你能聞到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,切 一直都是我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你也說幾句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,和我練習說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快點說點什麼吧 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是護送新娘的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,居然對喜慶的婚禮放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喜慶個屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐是被嫁給妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁給妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我必須要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊去 我射你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,方便的話跟我們說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們對妖怪略知一二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那邊有雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是殘雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以前就出現在附近吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以為了不讓它吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次給妖怪準備新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它就老實回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,之後每次出現都會準備新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不準備的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就會被屠村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪也想要人類的新娘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還要那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐說她們都被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不懂妖怪怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這次就是你姐姐被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要救出姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓妖怪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這時就該我們出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥幹掉過各式各樣的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那雲不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,當真?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不過不是免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不白做事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很香喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要值錢的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這是砂金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在河裡撿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那個的話還有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 成交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子 這是名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅也很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,才不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是個好名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快承認是好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說了不要來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我來救姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,為了村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他們為了自己把你犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我自願來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讓大家都被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,還有你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讓姐姐死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 那妖怪我們會收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣就萬事大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吃人的話肯定有嘴和肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就從那裡切開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥說交給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在趕緊逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸的視線裡滿是火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,周圍的雲也是妖怪的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,被火焰之牆包圍的百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次碰到什麼都看不到的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是你的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐不是我的親姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直是一個人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我小時候爸爸和媽媽就病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有這座山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我討厭人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說這不再是我的山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就把我趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你受傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是那個住在山裡的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,長得像猴子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不記得自己的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只要看著姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,飢餓和寒冷就都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,過去只有媽媽才對我這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那個姐姐是不是曾經是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒功夫在這哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須替姐姐報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的工作都是有始有終的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一起解決掉那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在那片雲裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥不能自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,必須靠我們自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那片雲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是比原來更大了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這是那傢伙的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,蜈蚣脫皮之後會變得更大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,更大?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比現在還大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,得到新娘之後不是應該乖乖回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒準因為白天的事情生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它的弱點是日光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把它從雲裡拉出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,應該就能打死它了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話我有一個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,做吧猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,消滅蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 姐姐的復仇戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喂這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是個大就強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的百足來追我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,為了姐姐的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大的火也燒不掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在陽光下融化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 這樣也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥斬到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他剛才做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被火焰之牆遮擋住視線的百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,憑藉著弓箭的聲音 確定了妖怪的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 我說話的地方就是它的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他在呼喚多羅羅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我旁邊就是它的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這次總算結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,尾巴上還有一個頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你活著太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥的鼻子恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著 這是你的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這石頭是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這附近有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要不是這種石頭 是砂金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那種亮晶晶的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有那些了 它們不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了你們 救我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你們接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在村子裡一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是一個人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了呢 猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得好好想一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 名字是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得你真像個姐姐一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,多羅羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個叫做氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才好像叫我「多羅羅」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字不錯吧
